Package: monthlyDS
Title: Monthly anomaly downscaling with Climate Imprint
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Stephen", "Sobie", email = "ssobie@uvic.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Monthly bias correction of daily model simulations using monthly 
             climatologies from a higher-resolution gridded dataset. The method
             is described in Sobie and Murdock (2017) <doi:10.1175/JAMC-D-16-0287.1>
             as applied using the PRISM dataset.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.3)
Imports: ncdf4, PCICt, utils
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
